Hi,

I am a regular pharmeasy customer. My order dated 07 Oct is on hold as I
learnt through sms & later the App. Kindly note

1. I uploaded the required prescription while ordering. In fact almost all
medicines are repeat.
2. They say they couldn't contact me? I see 2 missed call on my phone
8062491562, over 2 minutes, at 6.37 & 6.38 PM yesterday 07 December.  I
presume they are the missed calls from pharmeasy? In the first place I see
no reason for Doctors call or any call as only 1 item needed prescription
which I uploaded while ordering.
3. This morning, over last couple of hours, I have made several calls to
pharmeasy helpline but no call back yet.

In fact got a call back just now from helpline, as I was writing this mail.
When I asked why the order is on hold he said it's from confirmation team
and will expedite them for call back?

I continue to wait for the answers as well as further order processing.

Thanks & Regards
Kamal Sodhi
